&lt;p&gt;At Google DeepMind, we’re a team of scientists, engineers, machine learning experts and more, working together to advance the state of the&amp;nbsp;art in artificial intelligence. We use our technologies for widespread&amp;nbsp;public benefit and scientific discovery, and collaborate with others on&amp;nbsp;critical challenges, ensuring safety and ethics are the highest priority.&amp;nbsp;We don’t set limits based on what others think is possible or impossible.&amp;nbsp;We drive ourselves and inspire each other to push boundaries and&amp;nbsp;achieve ambitious goals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;The Area: Gemini App&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Gemini App is at the forefront of the AI revolution, bringing helpful,&amp;nbsp;generative AI experiences to users across the globe. We are seeking a&amp;nbsp;visionary Design Leader to lead the strategy that will define the future of&amp;nbsp;our product.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;The Role&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this critical role, you will be responsible for defining and visioning the&amp;nbsp;user experience, driving design excellence, and fostering a culture of&amp;nbsp;innovation across Gemini. You will work closely with product&amp;nbsp;management, engineering, and research teams to deliver an intuitive,&amp;nbsp;powerful, and aesthetically pleasing experience for the needs of users&amp;nbsp;globally.&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Distinguished Designer is the technical soul of the Gemini interface.&amp;nbsp;You are responsible for the bridge between cutting-edge machine&amp;nbsp;learning and pixel-perfect mobile implementation. You will architect the&amp;nbsp;systems that allow Gemini to feel &quot;as fast as thought&quot; while maintaining&amp;nbsp;world-class stability and performance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Architecting the AI-UI Bridge: Design the technical frameworks&amp;nbsp;for iOS and Android that handle non-deterministic AI outputs&amp;nbsp;(streaming audio/visuals) with zero jitter and maximum fluidity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Performance Engineering: Own the &quot;Gold Standard&quot; for mobile UI latency. You will optimize rendering and state management to handle complex multimodal requests without compromising battery life or device thermals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;AI-Augmented Tooling: Build and deploy internal &quot;Design-to-Code&quot; pipelines that allow the design team to use Gemini to automate UI generation and live-model prototyping.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Technical North Star: Establish UX best practices for emerging technologies or ambiguous problem spaces. Mentor senior individual contributors and engineers at the intersection of UI development and AI inference.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
