&lt;li&gt;Technical Mastery: Expert-level mastery of mobile frameworks (Flutter, Swift, Kotlin, or React Native) and front-end performance for real-time applications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leadership: Demonstrated track record of shipping and scaling flagship consumer applications across platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred background includes one or any combination of the following:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Master&#39;s degree or Ph.D. in a design-related field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with AI/ML and agentic technologies; Depth and breadth of knowledge that enables ideation and development of creative solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
